This paper deals with fair division of indivisible goods, which is a topic in computational social choice (cs.GT). The paper also proposes an algorithm for computing EFX allocations, which involves optimization and decision-making, making it relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the allocation, which is a topic in computational economics (cs.EC) and machine learning (cs.LG).
